  • Field Details

    • CurrentCellWalls

      private BitSet CurrentCellWalls
      CurrentCellWalls represents the cell walls and state. Bit 0 refers to the Active state, where 0 is active, and 1 is inactive Bit 1-4 refers to individual walls in the order, Left, Right, Up, Down. 1 represents a wall, and 0 represents no wall.
